      • isSafeDeleteAvailable

        public boolean isSafeDeleteAvailable(PsiElement element)
        Description copied from class: RefactoringSupportProvider
        Checks if the Safe Delete refactoring can be applied to the specified element in the language. The Safe Delete refactoring also requires the plugin to implement Find Usages functionality.
        Overrides:
        isSafeDeleteAvailable in class RefactoringSupportProvider
        Parameters:
        element - the element for which Safe Delete was invoked
        Returns:
        true if Safe Delete is available, false otherwise.
